          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">νίζω</span></b> , imp. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">νίζ</span>(<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ε</span>), ipf.
            <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">νίζον</span>, fut. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">νίψω</span>, aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">νίψα</span>, mid.
          ipf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">νίζετο</span>, aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">νιψάμην</span>, pass. perf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">νένιπται</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">wash, wash off</span>, mid., oneself or
          a part of oneself; w. two accusatives, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">νίψαι
