          mid., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χρόα ἅλμην</span>, ‘the brine from his
          person,’ <i><span class="en">Od. 6.224</span></i>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">; ἁλός</span>, ‘with water from the sea,’
            <i><span class="en">Od. 2.261</span></i>; pass., <i><span class="en">Il. 24.419</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
